  "local_port": 49820,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "How can I use my Jio 4G SIM ?",
  "response": "Using your Jio 4G SIM is straightforward. Here are the steps to get started:\n\n---\n\n### **1. Insert the Jio SIM into Your Phone**\n   - Ensure your phone is unlocked and supports 4G/LTE.\n   - Insert the Jio SIM card into the appropriate SIM slot.\n   - Restart your phone if necessary.\n\n---\n\n### **2. Activate Your Jio SIM**\n   - If the SIM is new, it should activate automatically when you insert it.\n   - If it doesn\u2019t activate, dial **59059** or send an SMS \"START\" to **199**.\n   - Follow the on-screen instructions to complete the activation process.\n\n---\n\n### **3. Set Up APN (Access Point Name)**\n   - Go to **Settings** > **Mobile Network** > **Access Point Names (APN)**.\n   - Add a new APN with the following details:\n     - Name: **Jio**\n     - APN: **jionet**\n     - Leave other fields blank or as default.\n     - Save and select this APN.\n\n---\n\n### **4. Make a Call**\n   - Call any number to test your connection.\n   - If calls don\u2019t work, ensure your phone is set to use 4G/LTE for voice calls (VoLTE). Most phones automatically detect this.\n\n---\n\n### **5. Use Mobile Data**\n   - Turn on mobile data in your phone\u2019s settings.\n   - Open a browser or app to check your internet connection.\n\n---\n\n### **6. Recharge Your Jio SIM**\n   - If your SIM doesn\u2019t have an active plan, recharge it using the **MyJio app** or by visiting **Jio's official website**.\n   - Choose a plan that suits your needs (calls, data, SMS, etc.).\n\n---\n\n### **7. Download the MyJio App**\n   - Download and install the **MyJio app** from the Google Play Store or Apple App Store.\n   - Log in with your Jio number to manage your account, check balance, recharge, and avail offers.\n\n---\n\n### **8. Troubleshooting**\n   - **No Signal**: Ensure your phone supports VoLTE and 4G/LTE.\n   - **Calls Not Working**: Contact Jio customer care (**198** or **199**) to check if VoLTE is enabled.\n   - **No Internet**: Verify the APN settings and ensure mobile data is turned on.\n\n---\n\nIf you face any issues, contact Jio customer care or visit a nearby Jio store for assistance. Enjoy your Jio services!",
  "temperature": 1.0,
